storyInfo: Gavial and the gang hold a swimming competition under the guise of surveying. Stitch, anxious about his design task, is encouraged to join by the industry representative.

attributes.content: Without further ado, let's begin the first joint Zeruertza-Acahualla-Rhodes Island swimming competition!
attributes.name: Croque Diamondface

attributes.content: I'm Croque Diamondface, Zeruertza's business representative. This broadcast is brought to you by Deculture Silvermint's newest high-definition camera.
attributes.name: Croque Diamondface

attributes.content: First, let's take a look at the course.
attributes.name: Croque Diamondface

attributes.content: The race will take place on an underground lake that stretches from here, all the way to the tunnel.
attributes.name: Croque Diamondface
Croque Diamondface
attributes.content: Here are the rules:

attributes.name: Croque Diamondface
attributes.content: Anything goes, and whoever gets to the other side of the lake first is the winner!
The winner will get an unlimited supply of my special craft ale for one month!
attributes.name: Croque Diamondface

attributes.content: The Rhodes Island representative is—
attributes.name: Croque Diamondface

attributes.content: The Wind of Iberia, Rhodes Island's sexiest man, Elysium!
attributes.name: Croque Diamondface

attributes.content: What's up, Durins?
attributes.name: Elysium

attributes.content: Was that introduction why he pulled Croque to the side to talk to her?
attributes.name: Inam

attributes.content: The Acahualla representative is—
attributes.name: Croque Diamondface

attributes.content: Gavial!
attributes.name: Croque Diamondface

attributes.content: Go for it, Gavial!
attributes.name: Tomimi

attributes.content: Hey everybody!
attributes.name: Gavial

attributes.content: And we have a surprise for the Zeruertza representative—
attributes.name: Croque Diamondface

attributes.content: Master Edge, our environment and climate representative!
attributes.name: Croque Diamondface

attributes.content: How did a tunnel survey turn into a swimming competition?
attributes.name: Avdotya

attributes.content: It's a rare opportunity, isn't it?
attributes.name: Gavial

attributes.content: We're still waiting on the equipment, after all.
attributes.name: Gavial

attributes.content: Plus, it's not easy to go back and forth with the railway out of operation. If we're going over anyway, we might as well do something fun with it.
attributes.name: Gavial

attributes.content: Sigh... have it your way.
attributes.name: Avdotya

attributes.content: Aren't you coming?
attributes.name: Gavial

attributes.content: Not interested. I would rather check up on Tomimi and Deculture's progress.
attributes.name: Avdotya

attributes.content: What a boring Ursus woman.
attributes.name: Gavial

attributes.content: I'm not Ursus!
attributes.name: Avdotya

attributes.content: And how did you convince Master Edge?
attributes.name: Avdotya

attributes.content: I volunteered, Avdotya.
attributes.name: Edge Eartheart

attributes.content: But...
attributes.name: Avdotya

attributes.content: I just wanted you to help me out while you're having fun.
attributes.name: Edge Eartheart

attributes.content: Now that you've helped me, I certainly won't object to this little event.
attributes.name: Edge Eartheart

attributes.content: We have plenty who like to play in the water, but not a single one who's actually a good swimmer.
attributes.name: Edge Eartheart

attributes.content: This is about the pride of Zeruertza, after all, so I've got to put this sack of old bones on the line.
attributes.name: Edge Eartheart

attributes.content: Don't sweat it, Master. It's all friendly competition.
attributes.name: Gavial

attributes.content: You say that, but I can't have people talking about how Zeruertza lost to a bunch of surface-dwellers!
attributes.name: Edge Eartheart

attributes.content: Avdotya said she's not interested. She didn't say she wouldn't do it.
attributes.name: Gavial

attributes.content: Durins aren't a pushy people. If she doesn't want to join, I won't force her.
attributes.name: Edge Eartheart

attributes.content: Plus, Avdotya isn't a native of Zeruertza. Makes sense she wouldn't want to represent us.
attributes.name: Edge Eartheart

attributes.content: Looks like it's up to me then.
attributes.name: Edge Eartheart

attributes.content: ...Alright, alright, I'll compete on behalf of the Durins!
attributes.name: Avdotya

attributes.content: Happy now?
attributes.name: Avdotya

attributes.content: Really?
attributes.name: Edge Eartheart

attributes.content: How can I not, after what you said?
attributes.name: Avdotya

attributes.content: That's more like it!
attributes.name: Gavial

attributes.content: Croque!
attributes.name: Edge Eartheart

attributes.content: Are you really going to participate, Avdotya?
attributes.name: Croque Diamondface

attributes.content: Is there a problem?
attributes.name: Avdotya

attributes.content: (Whisper) Unlimited supply of craft ale for one month. It will be a real hit for me if she wins this.
attributes.name: Croque Diamondface

attributes.content: Well, it's just friendly competition. No need to be too serious about it.
attributes.name: Croque Diamondface

attributes.content: I'll win this! For Zeruertza, and for the ale!
attributes.name: Avdotya

attributes.content: Er, alright, good luck.
attributes.name: Croque Diamondface

attributes.content: Excuse the interruption. We have an announcement to make.
attributes.name: Croque Diamondface

attributes.content: Avdotya will be subbing in for Master Edge as the representative of Zeruertza.
attributes.name: Croque Diamondface

attributes.content: Let's give her a round of applause!
attributes.name: Croque Diamondface

attributes.content: You still have to come with us across the river, though, Master Edge.
attributes.name: Gavial

attributes.content: How about you ride on my back during the competition? I'll take you across.
attributes.name: Gavial

attributes.content: Oh?
attributes.name: Edge Eartheart

attributes.content: Was that intended to be an insult, Gavial?
attributes.name: Avdotya

attributes.content: Hm? No.
attributes.name: Gavial

attributes.content: I just don't think I'll lose.
attributes.name: Gavial

attributes.content: Speaking of which, you should probably get changed if you're gonna race.
attributes.name: Gavial

attributes.content: Since you're carrying extra weight, these clothes will do just fine.
attributes.name: Avdotya

attributes.content: Oh?
attributes.name: Gavial

attributes.content: Just because I don't exercise often doesn't mean I'm out of shape.
attributes.name: Avdotya

attributes.content: I'm not so weak that I'll lose to a Sargon.
attributes.name: Avdotya

attributes.content: Ha. There it is, that's the face. Haven't seen you make a better one yet.
attributes.name: Gavial

attributes.content: Dúra.
attributes.name: Avdotya

attributes.content: Contestants, please take your positions.
attributes.name: Croque Diamondface

attributes.content: They're calling us.
attributes.name: Gavial

attributes.content: I have ears.
attributes.name: Avdotya

attributes.content: Maybe this isn't the best time to interrupt, but did they forget that I'm competing as well?
attributes.name: Elysium

attributes.content: Whatever. They'll find out who has the real skills when the action starts.
attributes.name: Elysium

attributes.content: On your marks.
attributes.name: Croque Diamondface

attributes.content: Ready.
attributes.name: Croque Diamondface

attributes.content: Hang on tight, Master Edge. Things could get a little rough once the race starts.
attributes.name: Gavial

attributes.content: Don't underestimate the wisdom of age.
attributes.name: Edge Eartheart

attributes.content: Get—
attributes.name: Croque Diamondface

attributes.content: Damn it, I got provoked into letting my Ursine slip.
attributes.name: Avdotya

attributes.content: I'll beat you, Gavial.
attributes.name: Avdotya

attributes.content: Set—
attributes.name: Croque Diamondface

attributes.content: Oh, come to think of it, I should have asked Croque to add the title 'Lone Ranger' to my name.
attributes.name: Elysium

attributes.content: I'll remember for next time.
attributes.name: Elysium

attributes.content: It just occurred to me... don't I have to follow them if I want to get a good angle with the camera?
attributes.name: Croque Diamondface

attributes.content: But I don't have a boat, and I can't exactly hold a camera while swimming. What do I do?
attributes.name: Croque Diamondface
Croque Diamondface
attributes.content: Ah well, never mind.

attributes.name: Croque Diamondface
attributes.content: Go!
At Croque's command, the three contestants — plus one passenger — leap into the water.
The race begins.
Gavial has taken the lead.
attributes.name: Announcement From Afar

attributes.content: Ever since she came to Zeruertza, Gavial has wowed us with her superb athleticism.
attributes.name: Announcement From Afar

attributes.content: She's gotten ahead of the pack, even with Master Edge on her back!
attributes.name: Announcement From Afar

attributes.content: They're having a little too much fun.
attributes.name: Stitch Canvas

attributes.content: Why don't you join them, Stitch Canvas?
attributes.name: Deculture Silvermint

attributes.content: Deculture?! Why are you here? Aren't you working on repairing the railway?
attributes.name: Stitch Canvas

attributes.content: No problem, I've put the bots to work there.
attributes.name: Deculture Silvermint

attributes.content: Keep your distance. I have Oripathy.
attributes.name: Stitch Canvas

attributes.content: Oripathy doesn't spread so easily, does it?
attributes.name: Deculture Silvermint

attributes.content: Plus, I like the peace and quiet of your place.
attributes.name: Deculture Silvermint

attributes.content: Well, there's a surprise. Gavial is still in the lead, as expected.
attributes.name: Announcement From Afar

attributes.content: But how many of us would have expected Avdotya to be hot on her tail?
attributes.name: Announcement From Afar

attributes.content: Who could have guessed that the elegant lady of Zeruertza has such power within her?
attributes.name: Announcement From Afar

attributes.content: She's keeping pace with Gavial, who hasn't been able to shake her.
attributes.name: Announcement From Afar

attributes.content: Oops, I can't see. Can someone give me a shoulder to stand on?
attributes.name: Announcement From Afar

attributes.content: There we go. Thanks.
attributes.name: Announcement From Afar

attributes.content: I've read in 'Stranger Things' that the people of Ursus are a hardy folk, able to live on nothing but ice for three months. I still didn't expect Avdotya to really keep pace with Gavial...
attributes.name: Stitch Canvas

attributes.content: You sure are interested in what's going on there. Why don't you go over and have a look?
attributes.name: Deculture Silvermint

attributes.content: Not interested. It's a waste of time.
attributes.name: Stitch Canvas

attributes.content: Really? You've hardly touched your sketch since the race started.
attributes.name: Deculture Silvermint

attributes.content: What do you want, Deculture?
attributes.name: Stitch Canvas

attributes.content: I'm just curious, Stitch. What's troubling you?
attributes.name: Deculture Silvermint

attributes.content: Because you felt like you deceived Gavial and her friends?
attributes.name: Deculture Silvermint

attributes.content: Things don't have to be so complicated. Everything will fall into place if you agree to fix the dome.
attributes.name: Deculture Silvermint

attributes.content: You don't want to fix the dome, so you're using the vote results as an excuse not to do it. Instead, you made the proposal to demolish the slide and repair the railway.
attributes.name: Deculture Silvermint

attributes.content: And I'm not wrong! Blowing up the slide and fixing the railway will allow us to detect the spread of active Originium!
attributes.name: Stitch Canvas

attributes.content: I didn't say you were wrong. While machine surveying of Originium has fallen out of fashion, the equipment we have is still usable.
attributes.name: Deculture Silvermint

attributes.content: Master Edge's problems will be solved once we build a boat and set things up.
attributes.name: Deculture Silvermint

attributes.content: He won't be pestering you about the dome anymore. You can continue your design work in this hut of yours, competing with Catch, and everybody lives happily ever after.
attributes.name: Deculture Silvermint

attributes.content: Why are you anxious?
attributes.name: Deculture Silvermint

attributes.content: What are you anxious about?
attributes.name: Deculture Silvermint

attributes.content: We're at the halfway point, 300m point.
attributes.name: Announcement From Afar

attributes.content: What's that? It's 400m already? Alright.
attributes.name: Announcement From Afar

attributes.content: Anyway, the order hasn't changed since the start of the race, with Gavial in the lead, Avdotya in second place, and Elysium in third.
attributes.name: Announcement From Afar

attributes.content: Al-though Elysium has not overtaken the others, his form is a thing of beauty!
attributes.name: Announcement From Afar

attributes.content: Is he staying in third place on purpose?
attributes.name: Announcement From Afar

attributes.content: I just feel uneasy.
attributes.name: Stitch Canvas

attributes.content: Like I've dumped everything on them.
attributes.name: Stitch Canvas

attributes.content: I agreed to compete with Catch on a design for a new Zeruertzan landmark... but how can I convince the people? I have no confidence there.
attributes.name: Stitch Canvas

attributes.content: You'll get along so much better with Catch if you're being honest about your feelings with him.
attributes.name: Deculture Silvermint

attributes.content: ...It won't happen.
attributes.name: Stitch Canvas

attributes.content: I'll never like him, and he'll never like me.
attributes.name: Stitch Canvas

attributes.content: Hm... well, I'm just looking for a place to take a break. It's none of my business if you want to keep staring at a blank piece of paper.
attributes.name: Deculture Silvermint

attributes.content: But if you want to check things out—
attributes.name: Deculture Silvermint

attributes.content: Deculture, Deculture. The first boat for the railway project is complete and ready by the lakeside.
attributes.name: Strange Machine #0429

attributes.content: The excavation and survey equipment that Master Edge asked for. You can help me deliver it.
attributes.name: Deculture Silvermint

attributes.content: Thanks.
attributes.name: Stitch Canvas

attributes.content: Deculture, Deculture, taking care of Stitch.
attributes.name: Strange Machine #0429

attributes.content: I'm not the only one taking care of him.
attributes.name: Deculture Silvermint

attributes.content: Well, I can take a nap now that he's gone.
attributes.name: Deculture Silvermint

attributes.content: I'll leave the rest to you and the surface-dwellers.
attributes.name: Deculture Silvermint

attributes.content: Do not worry. Zumama, our friend, will help. Do not worry.
attributes.name: Strange Machine #0429

attributes.content: You like her that much?
attributes.name: Deculture Silvermint

attributes.content: Zumama cares for us. We like Zumama.
attributes.name: Strange Machine #0429

attributes.content: What a strange surface-dweller.
attributes.name: Deculture Silvermint

attributes.content: We're here by the lake to get a better view!
attributes.name: Croque Diamondface Up High

attributes.content: Hey, is that Stitch the architect over there?
attributes.name: Croque Diamondface Up High

attributes.content: Wait, stop fidgeting! I'll lose my footing!
attributes.name: Croque Diamondface Up High

attributes.content: Whoa!!!
attributes.name: Croque Diamondface Up High

attributes.content: The Durins have made a Durin tower for Croque, so she can see the race better.
It is not easy to keep up a tower consisting of dozens of Durins, however, and it begins to lean at Croque's movement, eventually—
Ouch, my butt...
attributes.name: Croque Diamondface

attributes.content: The robot said the boat is parked around here.
attributes.name: Tomimi

attributes.content: This is the equipment that Master Edge asked for?
attributes.name: Tomimi

attributes.content: I'll load Gavial's equipment onto it as well, and ask someone to bring the boat across.
attributes.name: Tomimi

attributes.content: Hff... phew...
attributes.name: Stitch Canvas

attributes.content: This is the boat?
attributes.name: Stitch Canvas

attributes.content: Stitch? I think so.
attributes.name: Tomimi

attributes.content: Off I go then.
attributes.name: Stitch Canvas

attributes.content: Huh?
attributes.name: Tomimi

attributes.content: Oh, he just got onto the boat that the robots brought to the lakeside, and he's sailing across the lake!
attributes.name: Croque Diamondface

attributes.content: Did he come to join the competition?
attributes.name: Croque Diamondface

attributes.content: Come to think of it, the rules don't say you can't use vehicles!
attributes.name: Croque Diamondface
